  film in 1981 , simon adapted his play as a film with the title only when i laugh , starring his then - wife marsha mason in the lead role . " ' only when i laugh ' listing " internet movie database , accessed april 10 , 2012   according to susan fehrenbacher koprince ( associate professor of english at the university of north dakota , grand forks ) , the film " is radically changed " from the play , and used " less than half " of the play .

playwrights : his lesser - known plays include " fools " , " god 's favorite " & " the gingerbread lady "

